  cutsceneName: Intro
  lines:
  - image: {fileID: 0}
    text: You are a PENR Dispatcher assigned to the city of Minglanilla, Cebu.
  - image: {fileID: 0}
    text: "Minglanilla is a city nestled deep within one of the region\u2019s last
      remaining forested frontiers."
  - image: {fileID: 0}
    text: Illegal loggers close in, forest fires rage unchecked, and environmental
      pressures mount.
  - image: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 93200a5ec75906c4998456fede0bb60d, type: 3}
    text: You have been tasked to watch over its forests. In other words...
  - image: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 607a2828a60783d4d90555cb2743390f, type: 3}
    text: "\"what are we, some kinda GroveWatch\u2122?\""
  - image: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 93200a5ec75906c4998456fede0bb60d, type: 3}
    text: You are the final line of defense. Welcome to GroveWatch!
  onComplete: 0
